data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!!! Great investment opportunity in the charming town of Columbiana! Full brick 3 bed 2 bath with 2 additional heated/cooled rooms in the basement and a 2 car garage. This property has endless potential, just needs to be rehabbed. Just minutes away from downtown Columbiana shopping and entertainment district. New HVAC in February 2023, Roof replaced in 2010.
